  "text": "Let \u03b7(D \u00b5\u2297E sig,u (r)) be the reduced \u03b7-invariant in the sense of Atiyah-PatodiSinger [CITATION_1] . More precisely, for s \u2208 C, Re(s) \u2265 p, set",
